{"title":"Manjaro常用配置和软件","slug":"Manjaro常用配置和软件","date":"2021-02-26T08:13:00.000Z","updated":"2021-02-26T08:13:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Manjaro常用配置和软件.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/5267fc1e20ca7cbca297d44d51d5607c.png","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/0ae273b93242e469f7e0e420c29d5df1.png","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/1dc430f80147fffd21cf49ecff0a26b2.png"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/5267fc1e20ca7cbca297d44d51d5607c.png\" alt=\"manjaro\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"1-换源\"><a href=\"#1-换源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 换源\"></a>1. 换源</h1><p>启动konsole， 输入以下指令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在弹出框内选择一个源就好了</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-软件\"><a href=\"#2-软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 软件\"></a>2. 软件</h1><h2 id=\"1-yay-amp-yaourt-amp-pacman\"><a href=\"#1-yay-amp-yaourt-amp-pacman\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. yay &amp; yaourt &amp; pacman\"></a>1. yay &amp; yaourt &amp; pacman</h2><h3 id=\"yay\"><a href=\"#yay\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"yay\"></a>yay</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>切换清华源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay --aururl <span class=\"string\">\"https://aur.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn\"</span> --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>可以替代 <code>sudo pacman</code>为<code>yay</code>就可以了，跟pacman一样使用<br>yay -Ss可以查询软件库中的软件</p>\n<h3 id=\"yaourt\"><a href=\"#yaourt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"yaourt\"></a>yaourt</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -S yaourt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"pacman\"><a href=\"#pacman\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pacman\"></a>pacman</h3><ol>\n<li>查找本地软件包 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Q [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>查询已经安装的软件包 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Qs [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>远程仓库包查询 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -S [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>根据名称查询远程仓库 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Ss [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>升级系统及软件包 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Syu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>删除软件包并保留依赖 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -R [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>删除软件包并删除依赖 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Rs [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-输入法\"><a href=\"#2-输入法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 输入法\"></a>2. 输入法</h2>google拼音<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx-im fcitx-configtool fcitx-googlepinyin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n下载完成后需要配置fcitx5的环境变量<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ～/.xprofile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n在里面输入<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> GTK_IM_MODULE=fictx</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> XMODIFIERS=<span class=\"string\">\"@im=fcitx\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n然后reboot重启就好了<h2 id=\"3-截图工具\"><a href=\"#3-截图工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 截图工具\"></a>3. 截图工具</h2>首推flameshot， 类似于win上的snipaste, 也可以使用深度截图<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S flameshot</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 深度截图</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S deepin-screenshot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"配置快捷键\"><a href=\"#配置快捷键\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置快捷键\"></a>配置快捷键</h3>打开系统设置里面的快捷键，选择自定义快捷键<br><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/0ae273b93242e469f7e0e420c29d5df1.png\" alt=\"\"><br><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/a3206b0172d9a2bfe7cd86b024c9c115.png\" alt=\"\"><br>动作路径就是启动flameshot的gui， 路径是<code>/usr/bin/flameshot gui</code><br>然后应用就可以使用 <code>print</code>键进行截图了<h2 id=\"4-终端\"><a href=\"#4-终端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 终端\"></a>4. 终端</h2><h3 id=\"1-zsh\"><a href=\"#1-zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. zsh\"></a>1. zsh</h3>修改shell为zsh<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chsh -s /usr/bin/zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n安装oh-my-zsh<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh -c <span class=\"string\">\"<span class=\"variable\">$(wget https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)</span>\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sh -c <span class=\"string\">\"<span class=\"variable\">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)</span>\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-fish\"><a href=\"#2-fish\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. fish\"></a>2. fish</h3>安装<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n修改默认shell为fish<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chsh -s /usr/bin/fish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\nfish也有对应的oh-my-fish<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -L https://get.oh-my.fish | fish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n安装完成后, 输入fish进入fish<br><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/1dc430f80147fffd21cf49ecff0a26b2.png\" alt=\"fish\"><br>输入<code>fish_config</code>就可以启动一个配置服务, 会自动打开一个网页, 在里面进行自定义的美化<br><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/77750ea6757e1829ca6e4cfedb41b53f.png\" alt=\"fish_config\"></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>基本使用</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">omf update [omf] […] <span class=\"comment\"># omf更新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf install [|] <span class=\"comment\"># 安装 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 如安装wttr天气组件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf install wttr</span><br><span class=\"line\">omf repositories [list|add|remove] <span class=\"comment\"># 管理用户安装的包仓库</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf list <span class=\"comment\"># 显示安装的包</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 设置主题，可查看主题列表https://github.com/oh-my-fish/oh-my-fish/blob/master/docs/Themes.md</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf theme </span><br><span class=\"line\">omf remove <span class=\"comment\"># 移除</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf reload <span class=\"comment\"># 重载omf</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf search -t|–theme / -p|–package <span class=\"comment\"># 搜索主题或者包</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf channel</span><br><span class=\"line\">omf doctor <span class=\"comment\"># doctor, 医生, 检查</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf destroy <span class=\"comment\"># 删除omf</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"5-开发\"><a href=\"#5-开发\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 开发\"></a>5. 开发</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S google-chrome </span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S chromium</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># vscode </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -S code</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S git vim docker npm node yarn</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 卸载JDK8 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -R jre8-openjdk-headless jre8-openjdk jdk8-openjdk</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装JDK11 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S jdk11-openjdk </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># vscodium </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S vscodium-bin </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># JetBrains IDE </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S intellij-idea-ultimate-edition webstorm</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># FTP/SFTP</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S filezilla</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># postman  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S postman</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改<code>npm</code>和<code>yarn</code>源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org/ </span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"6-日常\"><a href=\"#6-日常\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. 日常\"></a>6. 日常</h2><h3 id=\"office\"><a href=\"#office\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"office\"></a>office</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S wps-office</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S ttf-wps-fonts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"福昕阅读器\"><a href=\"#福昕阅读器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"福昕阅读器\"></a>福昕阅读器</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S foxitreader</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"网易云音乐\"><a href=\"#网易云音乐\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网易云音乐\"></a>网易云音乐</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S netease-cloud-music</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"typora\"><a href=\"#typora\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"typora\"></a>typora</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yaourt typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"字体\"><a href=\"#字体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字体\"></a>字体</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S ttf-roboto noto-fonts ttf-dejavu</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 文泉驿</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S wqy-bitmapfont wqy-microhei wqy-microhei-lite wqy-zenhei</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装 wqy-bitmapfont 和 wqy-zenhei 可解决 manjaro18 xfce版 终端字体间距过大的问题，重启终端即可。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 思源字体</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-code-pro-fonts </span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-sans-pro-fonts</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-serif-pro-fonts</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-han-sans-cn-fonts    </span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-han-serif-cn-fonts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"QQ-amp-微信\"><a href=\"#QQ-amp-微信\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"QQ &amp; 微信\"></a>QQ &amp; 微信</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S deepin-wine-tim     <span class=\"comment\"># qq</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S deepin-wine-wechat  <span class=\"comment\"># 微信</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"问题\"><a href=\"#问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题\"></a>问题</h1><p>在安装中出现过：</p>\n<h2 id=\"问题1\"><a href=\"#问题1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题1\"></a>问题1</h2><p><code>Cannot find the strip binary required for object file stripping.</code></p>\n<p>问题: 缺少二进制相关的东西</p>\n<p>解决</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -Sy base-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"问题2\"><a href=\"#问题2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题2\"></a>问题2</h2><p><code>[hls@k401uqk ~]$ yay -S xmind Rate limit reached</code></p>\n<p>原本是使用清华源的, 然后一直出这个问题, 最后切换回原来的源就可以了</p>\n<p>换回官方源即可解决</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay --aururl <span class=\"string\">\"https://aur.archlinux.org/\"</span> --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","more":"<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/5267fc1e20ca7cbca297d44d51d5607c.png\" alt=\"manjaro\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"1-换源\"><a href=\"#1-换源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 换源\"></a>1. 换源</h1><p>启动konsole， 输入以下指令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在弹出框内选择一个源就好了</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-软件\"><a href=\"#2-软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 软件\"></a>2. 软件</h1><h2 id=\"1-yay-amp-yaourt-amp-pacman\"><a href=\"#1-yay-amp-yaourt-amp-pacman\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. yay &amp; yaourt &amp; pacman\"></a>1. yay &amp; yaourt &amp; pacman</h2><h3 id=\"yay\"><a href=\"#yay\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"yay\"></a>yay</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>切换清华源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay --aururl <span class=\"string\">\"https://aur.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn\"</span> --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>可以替代 <code>sudo pacman</code>为<code>yay</code>就可以了，跟pacman一样使用<br>yay -Ss可以查询软件库中的软件</p>\n<h3 id=\"yaourt\"><a href=\"#yaourt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"yaourt\"></a>yaourt</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -S yaourt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"pacman\"><a href=\"#pacman\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pacman\"></a>pacman</h3><ol>\n<li>查找本地软件包 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Q [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>查询已经安装的软件包 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Qs [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>远程仓库包查询 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -S [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>根据名称查询远程仓库 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Ss [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>升级系统及软件包 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Syu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>删除软件包并保留依赖 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -R [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>删除软件包并删除依赖 <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pacman -Rs [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-输入法\"><a href=\"#2-输入法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 输入法\"></a>2. 输入法</h2>google拼音<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx-im fcitx-configtool fcitx-googlepinyin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n下载完成后需要配置fcitx5的环境变量<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ～/.xprofile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n在里面输入<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> GTK_IM_MODULE=fictx</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> XMODIFIERS=<span class=\"string\">\"@im=fcitx\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n然后reboot重启就好了<h2 id=\"3-截图工具\"><a href=\"#3-截图工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 截图工具\"></a>3. 截图工具</h2>首推flameshot， 类似于win上的snipaste, 也可以使用深度截图<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S flameshot</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 深度截图</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S deepin-screenshot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"配置快捷键\"><a href=\"#配置快捷键\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置快捷键\"></a>配置快捷键</h3>打开系统设置里面的快捷键，选择自定义快捷键<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/0ae273b93242e469f7e0e420c29d5df1.png\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/a3206b0172d9a2bfe7cd86b024c9c115.png\" alt=\"\"><br>动作路径就是启动flameshot的gui， 路径是<code>/usr/bin/flameshot gui</code><br>然后应用就可以使用 <code>print</code>键进行截图了<h2 id=\"4-终端\"><a href=\"#4-终端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 终端\"></a>4. 终端</h2><h3 id=\"1-zsh\"><a href=\"#1-zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. zsh\"></a>1. zsh</h3>修改shell为zsh<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chsh -s /usr/bin/zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n安装oh-my-zsh<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh -c <span class=\"string\">\"<span class=\"variable\">$(wget https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)</span>\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sh -c <span class=\"string\">\"<span class=\"variable\">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)</span>\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-fish\"><a href=\"#2-fish\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. fish\"></a>2. fish</h3>安装<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n修改默认shell为fish<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chsh -s /usr/bin/fish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\nfish也有对应的oh-my-fish<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -L https://get.oh-my.fish | fish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n安装完成后, 输入fish进入fish<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/1dc430f80147fffd21cf49ecff0a26b2.png\" alt=\"fish\"><br>输入<code>fish_config</code>就可以启动一个配置服务, 会自动打开一个网页, 在里面进行自定义的美化<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/77750ea6757e1829ca6e4cfedb41b53f.png\" alt=\"fish_config\"></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>基本使用</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">omf update [omf] […] <span class=\"comment\"># omf更新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf install [|] <span class=\"comment\"># 安装 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 如安装wttr天气组件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf install wttr</span><br><span class=\"line\">omf repositories [list|add|remove] <span class=\"comment\"># 管理用户安装的包仓库</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf list <span class=\"comment\"># 显示安装的包</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 设置主题，可查看主题列表https://github.com/oh-my-fish/oh-my-fish/blob/master/docs/Themes.md</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf theme </span><br><span class=\"line\">omf remove <span class=\"comment\"># 移除</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf reload <span class=\"comment\"># 重载omf</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf search -t|–theme / -p|–package <span class=\"comment\"># 搜索主题或者包</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf channel</span><br><span class=\"line\">omf doctor <span class=\"comment\"># doctor, 医生, 检查</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">omf destroy <span class=\"comment\"># 删除omf</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"5-开发\"><a href=\"#5-开发\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 开发\"></a>5. 开发</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S google-chrome </span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S chromium</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># vscode </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -S code</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S git vim docker npm node yarn</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 卸载JDK8 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -R jre8-openjdk-headless jre8-openjdk jdk8-openjdk</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装JDK11 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S jdk11-openjdk </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># vscodium </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S vscodium-bin </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># JetBrains IDE </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S intellij-idea-ultimate-edition webstorm</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># FTP/SFTP</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S filezilla</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># postman  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S postman</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改<code>npm</code>和<code>yarn</code>源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org/ </span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"6-日常\"><a href=\"#6-日常\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. 日常\"></a>6. 日常</h2><h3 id=\"office\"><a href=\"#office\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"office\"></a>office</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S wps-office</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S ttf-wps-fonts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"福昕阅读器\"><a href=\"#福昕阅读器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"福昕阅读器\"></a>福昕阅读器</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S foxitreader</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"网易云音乐\"><a href=\"#网易云音乐\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网易云音乐\"></a>网易云音乐</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S netease-cloud-music</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"typora\"><a href=\"#typora\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"typora\"></a>typora</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yaourt typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"字体\"><a href=\"#字体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字体\"></a>字体</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S ttf-roboto noto-fonts ttf-dejavu</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 文泉驿</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S wqy-bitmapfont wqy-microhei wqy-microhei-lite wqy-zenhei</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装 wqy-bitmapfont 和 wqy-zenhei 可解决 manjaro18 xfce版 终端字体间距过大的问题，重启终端即可。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 思源字体</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-code-pro-fonts </span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-sans-pro-fonts</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-serif-pro-fonts</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-han-sans-cn-fonts    </span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-han-serif-cn-fonts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"QQ-amp-微信\"><a href=\"#QQ-amp-微信\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"QQ &amp; 微信\"></a>QQ &amp; 微信</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S deepin-wine-tim     <span class=\"comment\"># qq</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S deepin-wine-wechat  <span class=\"comment\"># 微信</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"问题\"><a href=\"#问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题\"></a>问题</h1><p>在安装中出现过：</p>\n<h2 id=\"问题1\"><a href=\"#问题1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题1\"></a>问题1</h2><p><code>Cannot find the strip binary required for object file stripping.</code></p>\n<p>问题: 缺少二进制相关的东西</p>\n<p>解决</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -Sy base-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"问题2\"><a href=\"#问题2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题2\"></a>问题2</h2><p><code>[hls@k401uqk ~]$ yay -S xmind Rate limit reached</code></p>\n<p>原本是使用清华源的, 然后一直出这个问题, 最后切换回原来的源就可以了</p>\n<p>换回官方源即可解决</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay --aururl <span class=\"string\">\"https://aur.archlinux.org/\"</span> --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[{"name":"Linux","path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Manjaro","path":"api/tags/Manjaro.json"}]}